The Silent Party wave is one that has been sweeping the hottest cities in the U.S. - from Chicago, to Atlanta, to Los Angeles and back. Urban Fêtes and Millennium Age are bringing the party wave back to where it all began in the Windy City to ring in the Silent Party BLACK OUT Edition on Black Friday! Join us Friday, November 25th, at the one and only Reggies Live in Chicago, as we pick up a pair of headphones and jam out to our favorite records.

At our signature Silent Parties, the party-goer is in total control of their musical and social environment. Every attendee gets their own pair of headphones to tune in to whichever genre of music they prefer, with live DJs spinning each channel. It’s a unique experience to be part of a huge party that makes virtually no noise, except on social media afterward. The Black Friday Edition will feature special guests, a dance battle and more.
